SUMMARY:Peacetown continues at HopMonk with The Familiar Strangers
DESCRIPTION:The Familiar Strangers play an Americana grab bag of roots music from western swing to classic country\, blues rock\, swing jazz and even a little bit of gypsy jazz! Imagine Bob Wills and John Hiatt get in a car with Chuck Berry and they pick up a hitch hiking Dolly Parton! It’s kinda like that! \nThe band is comprised of top shelf veterans of the Bay Area music scene. Drawing from such well known bands/performers as Commander Cody\, Maria Muldaur\, Mad Maggies\, Laughing Gravy\, San Geronimo\, The Rhythm Rangers\, Clint Black\, Shirley Bassey & more. \nCandy Girard – fiddle\, vocals & killer smile\nMatt Davis – bass\, vocals & infectious friendliness\nKevin Russell – guitar\, vocals & set list maker\nTim Gahagan – percussion\, drums\, snappy dresser\nSean Allen – guitar super star! \nCome on out and join us for a fun evening!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/peacetown-continues-at-hopmonk-with-the-familiar-strangers-2/
LOCATION:HopMonk Tavern – Sebastopol\, 230 Petaluma Ave\, Sebastopol\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.4012;-122.823
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=HopMonk Tavern – Sebastopol 230 Petaluma Ave Sebastopol CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=230 Petaluma Ave:geo:-122.823,38.4012
END:VEVENT
