SUMMARY:A Night of Poetry and Community
DESCRIPTION:Russian River Books and Letters presents an evening of poetry\, featuring local West Sonoma County poets\, Robert Jones and Shawna Swetech\, followed by an Open Mic. Robert Jones will be reading from his new book\, “West of Sonoma County\,” poems that capture the essence of life in West Sonoma County. Shawna Swetech will be reading from her book\, “Standing in Their Fire.” (Kelsay Books\, 2026) Her collection is based on her 35 year career as a bedside hospital nurse. Sign up for Open Mic at the event\, one poem/3minutes per reader. \nRussian River Books and Letters\, 14045 Armstrong Woods Rd\, Guerneville\, CA
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/a-night-of-poetry-and-community/
LOCATION:Russian River Books and Letters\, 14045 Armstrong Woods Road\, Suite B\, Guerneville\, CA
CATEGORIES:Other
GEO:38.50307;-122.99721
