SUMMARY:First Thursdays Art Walk Sonoma
DESCRIPTION:Arts Guild Sonoma hosts FIRST THURSDAYS ARTWALK! Come to downtown Sonoma and enjoy the many storefronts\, tasting rooms\, and Art Galleries presenting all kinds of art mediums. Spend some time on the square afterwards\, bring a picnic\, or grab a bite at one of our delicious restaurants. With the temperature just about perfect\, you’ll enjoy the vibe of this quaint town.
